<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cartones Mágicos</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/index.css">
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/9b2fedeb7f.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/favicon.png" type="image/x-icon">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    
    <%- include("./includes/navbar") %>

  </header>
  <main>
    <div class="video-container">
      <div class="header-video">
        <video src="/videos/video.mp4" muted autoplay loop></video>
      </div>
      <div class="header-overlay"></div>
      <div class="header-content">
        <h1>Cartones Mágicos</h1>
        <p>Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dicta dolores temporibus eveniet modi sapiente quos neque ratione culpa nobis quisquam, explicabo rem odio laborum eligendi est dolorum reprehenderit fugit! Sapiente ad mollitia, natus quaerat quo incidunt ullam ipsa numquam repellendus impedit enim a est, aperiam saepe necessitatibus vel ducimus dolor!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <section class="section1">
      <div class="container-xxl">
        <div class="row row-gap-5 py-5 text-center">
          <div class="col-12">
            <article>
              <h2>Collectors</h2>
              <hr class="mx-auto">
            </article>
          </div>
          <div class="row row-gap-5 py-5">
            <% result.forEach((elem) => { %>
              <div class="col-8 col-md-4 mx-auto mx-md-0 d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center gap-3">
                <article class="collector-article">
                  <div class="collector-card">
                    <img class="mb-0 object-fit-cover" src="/images/collector/<%= elem.collector_img %>" alt="immagen collector">
                    <div class="tarjeta">
                      <h3><%= elem.collector_name %></h3>
                      <p><%= elem.interest_in %></p>
                      <button onclick="window.location.href='/collector/oneCollector/<%= elem.collector_id %>'" class="general-button">Info</button>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </article>
              </div>
              <% }) %>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <%- include("./includes/footer") %>
  
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>